"mh35902\"></a><figure class=\"topicIcon\"><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/40ff588be3beaa4acaf19d4beeba4177.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"30\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/AppIconTopic_Passwords.png\"></figure><h1>Reset your Mac login password</h1><p>Sometimes a login password needs to be reset—for example, if you have forgotten the login password and can’t use a password hint to remember it.</p><figure><picture><source media=\"(not all)\" srcset=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/d3e3f0b54d209b80c8103fe2b864a0ce.png\" originalImageName=\"Art/S2130_MacLogin~dark.png\"></source><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/802f844a595e0b0ea22dfaa0968c7a44.png\" alt=\"The Mac login screen, showing your password hint and instructions for resetting your password.\" height=\"498\" width=\"444\" originalImageName=\"Art/S2130_MacLogin.png\"></picture></figure><div id=\"mchlpa6c3711\" class=\"Task\"><h2 aria-controls=\"aria-mchlpa6c3711\" class=\"Name\">Reset your login password using your Apple ID</h2><div class=\"TaskBody\" role=\"region\" aria-hidden=\"false\" id=\"aria-mchlpa6c3711\"><p>If you associated your user account with your <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=apple-id&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=GLOSBDC8E694&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0&amp;aside=true\" class=\"xRef Aside\">Apple ID</a>, you can use your Apple ID to reset your login password.</p><ol><li><p>Click the question mark <img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/c6819a17cee376a243a4eb4cde38e097.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"30\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_QuestionMarkCircleGray.png\"> next to the password field.</p><p>If you don’t see a question mark <span class=\"NoBreak\"><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/c6819a17cee376a243a4eb4cde38e097.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"30\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_QuestionMarkCircleGray.png\">, </span>press and hold the power button until your Mac shuts down, then press the power button to restart your Mac.</p></li><li><p>Click the arrow <img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/52b86434894ad1df8fdab9137ffc910d.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"30\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_ArrowForwardCircleFill.png\"> next to “reset it using your Apple ID.”</p><p>If you don’t see an arrow <span class=\"NoBreak\"><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/52b86434894ad1df8fdab9137ffc910d.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"30\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_ArrowForwardCircleFill.png\">, </span>see the Apple Support article <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/HT212190\" class=\"URL\">If you can’t reset your Mac login password</a>.</p></li><li><p>Enter an Apple ID and password, then click Next.</p><p>Follow the instructions to reset your login password.</p></li></ol><p>If you don’t remember your Apple ID password, see <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=if-you-forget-your-apple-id-or-password&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHLCA50AA6A&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">If you forget your Apple ID or password</a>.</p></div></div><div id=\"apd83de6a1ac2764\" class=\"Task\"><h2 aria-controls=\"aria-apd83de6a1ac2764\" class=\"Name\">Reset your login password using a recovery key</h2><div class=\"TaskBody\" role=\"region\" aria-hidden=\"false\" id=\"aria-apd83de6a1ac2764\"><p>If you turned on FileVault encryption and created a recovery key, you can use the recovery key to reset your login password.</p><ol><li><p>Click the question mark <img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/c6819a17cee376a243a4eb4cde38e097.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"30\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_QuestionMarkCircleGray.png\"> next to the password field.</p><p>If you don’t see a question mark <span class=\"NoBreak\"><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/c6819a17cee376a243a4eb4cde38e097.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"30\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_QuestionMarkCircleGray.png\">, </span>press and hold the power button until your Mac shuts down, then press the power button to restart your Mac.</p></li><li><p>Click the arrow <img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/52b86434894ad1df8fdab9137ffc910d.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"30\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_ArrowForwardCircleFill.png\"> next to “reset it using your recovery key.”</p><p>If you don’t see an arrow <span class=\"NoBreak\"><img src=\"https://help.apple.com/assets/63BCA927AAE78C58DD7FBE35/63BCA92EAAE78C58DD7FBE76/en_US/52b86434894ad1df8fdab9137ffc910d.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"30\" width=\"30\" originalImageName=\"SharedGlobalArt/IL_ArrowForwardCircleFill.png\">, </span>see the Apple Support article <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/HT212190\" class=\"URL\">If you can’t reset your Mac login password</a>.</p></li><li><p>Enter the recovery key, then click Next.</p><p>Follow the instructions to reset your login password.</p></li></ol></div></div><p>When a user’s login password is reset, a new default <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=keychain&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=GLOS5BB3F38D&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0&amp;aside=true\" class=\"xRef Aside\">keychain</a> is created to store the user’s passwords. See <a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=about-your-keychain-password&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHLP1086&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">About your keychain password</a>.</p><div class=\"LinkUniversal\"><strong>See also</strong><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=change-the-login-password-on-mac&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MCHLP1550&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Change the login password on Mac</a><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/guide/?platform=mac&amp;product=mac-help&amp;vanityname=create-an-apple-id&amp;version=13.0&amp;locale=en_US&amp;topicid=MH35903&amp;type=ddm&amp;platformOSVersion=13.0\" class=\"xRef AppleTopic\">Create an Apple ID on Mac</a><a href=\"https://support.apple.com/HT204106\" class=\"URL\">Apple Support article: If your Apple ID is locked or disabled</a></div></body>","tags":[{"type":"audience","refKey":"PUBLIC_USERS","tagPath":"audience/PUBLIC_USERS","title":"Public"}]}]},"categoryInfo":{"categories":["IP-Meta/DesignVersion/DesignVersion2","platform/mac","DisplayVersion/macOS Ventura 13","MetaFollow/MetaFollowOFF","ContentMode/liveContent","SupportSearchIndex/SupportSearchIndexON","ArchivalStatus/Archived","ExternalIndex/ExternalIndexOFF"],"categoryDictionaries":[{"key":"SupportSearchIndexON","name":"SupportSearchIndexON","englishName":"SupportSearchIndexON","displayName":"SupportSearchIndexON","articleCount":"120736"},{"key":"liveContent","name":"Live Content","englishName":"Live Content","displayName":"Live Content","articleCount":"135880"},{"key":"IP-Meta","name":"IP-Meta","englishName":"IP-Meta","displayName":"IP-Meta","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"ContentMode","name":"ContentMode","englishName":"ContentMode","displayName":"ContentMode","articleCount":"0"},{"key":"DesignVersion2","name":"DesignVersion 2","englishName":"DesignVersion 2","di